description:
Add the subtle dotted/polka dot background pattern that appears across all pages on nuefunnel.com.

CSS implementation:
```css
body {
  background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 24px 24px;
  background-color: #FFFFFF;
}
```

This creates light gray dots (~8% opacity) on a 24px grid.

File: src/styles/global.css
